044   /** Default value */

047   /**

053      return new Builder();
054   }

073      return create().on(on);

075
076   /**
077    * Returns <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
078    *
079    * @param a The annotation to check.
080    * @return <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
081    */
082   public static boolean empty(Schema a) {
083      return a == null || DEFAULT.equals(a);
084   }
085
086   /**
087    * Converts the specified <ja>@Schema</ja> annotation into a generic map.
088    *
089    * @param a The annotation instance.  Can be <jk>null</jk>.
090    * @return The schema converted to a map, or and empty map if the annotation was null.
091    * @throws ParseException Malformed input encountered.
092    */
093   public static JsonMap asMap(Schema a) throws ParseException {
094      if (a == null)
095         return JsonMap.EMPTY_MAP;
096      JsonMap m = new JsonMap();
097      if (SchemaAnnotation.empty(a))
098         return m;
099      Predicate<String> ne = StringUtils::isNotEmpty;
100      Predicate<Collection<?>> nec = CollectionUtils::isNotEmpty;
101      Predicate<Map<?,?>> nem = CollectionUtils::isNotEmpty;
102      Predicate<Boolean> nf = ObjectUtils::isTrue;
103      Predicate<Long> nm1 = ObjectUtils::isNotMinusOne;
104      return m
105         .appendIf(nem, "additionalProperties", parseMap(a.additionalProperties()))
106         .appendIf(ne, "allOf", joinnl(a.allOf()))
107         .appendFirst(ne, "collectionFormat", a.collectionFormat(), a.cf())
108         .appendIf(ne, "default", joinnl(a._default(), a.df()))
109         .appendIf(ne, "discriminator", a.discriminator())
110         .appendIf(ne, "description", joinnl(a.description(), a.d()))
111         .appendFirst(nec, "enum", parseSet(a._enum()), parseSet(a.e()))
112         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMaximum", a.exclusiveMaximum() || a.emax())
113         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMinimum", a.exclusiveMinimum() || a.emin())
114         .appendIf(nem, "externalDocs", ExternalDocsAnnotation.merge(m.getMap("externalDocs"), a.externalDocs()))
115         .appendFirst(ne, "format", a.format(), a.f())
116         .appendIf(ne, "ignore", a.ignore() ? "true" : null)
117         .appendIf(nem, "items", merge(m.getMap("items"), a.items()))
118         .appendFirst(ne, "maximum", a.maximum(), a.max())
119         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxItems", a.maxItems(), a.maxi())
120         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxLength", a.maxLength(), a.maxl())
121         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxProperties", a.maxProperties(), a.maxp())
122         .appendFirst(ne, "minimum", a.minimum(), a.min())
123         .appendFirst(nm1, "minItems", a.minItems(), a.mini())
124         .appendFirst(nm1, "minLength", a.minLength(), a.minl())
125         .appendFirst(nm1, "minProperties", a.minProperties(), a.minp())
126         .appendFirst(ne, "multipleOf", a.multipleOf(), a.mo())
127         .appendFirst(ne, "pattern", a.pattern(), a.p())
128         .appendIf(nem, "properties", parseMap(a.properties()))
129         .appendIf(nf, "readOnly", a.readOnly() || a.ro())
130         .appendIf(nf, "required", a.required() || a.r())
131         .appendIf(ne, "title", a.title())
132         .appendFirst(ne, "type", a.type(), a.t())
133         .appendIf(nf, "uniqueItems", a.uniqueItems() || a.ui())
134         .appendIf(ne, "xml", joinnl(a.xml()))
135         .appendIf(ne, "$ref", a.$ref())
136      ;
137   }
138
139   private static JsonMap merge(JsonMap m, Items a) throws ParseException {
140      if (ItemsAnnotation.empty(a))
141         return m;
142      Predicate<String> ne = StringUtils::isNotEmpty;
143      Predicate<Collection<?>> nec = CollectionUtils::isNotEmpty;
144      Predicate<Map<?,?>> nem = CollectionUtils::isNotEmpty;
145      Predicate<Boolean> nf = ObjectUtils::isTrue;
146      Predicate<Long> nm1 = ObjectUtils::isNotMinusOne;
147      return m
148         .appendFirst(ne, "collectionFormat", a.collectionFormat(), a.cf())
149         .appendIf(ne, "default", joinnl(a._default(), a.df()))
150         .appendFirst(nec, "enum", parseSet(a._enum()), parseSet(a.e()))
151         .appendFirst(ne, "format", a.format(), a.f())
152         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMaximum", a.exclusiveMaximum() || a.emax())
153         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMinimum", a.exclusiveMinimum() || a.emin())
154         .appendIf(nem, "items", SubItemsAnnotation.merge(m.getMap("items"), a.items()))
155         .appendFirst(ne, "maximum", a.maximum(), a.max())
156         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxItems", a.maxItems(), a.maxi())
157         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxLength", a.maxLength(), a.maxl())
158         .appendFirst(ne, "minimum", a.minimum(), a.min())
159         .appendFirst(nm1, "minItems", a.minItems(), a.mini())
160         .appendFirst(nm1, "minLength", a.minLength(), a.minl())
161         .appendFirst(ne, "multipleOf", a.multipleOf(), a.mo())
162         .appendFirst(ne, "pattern", a.pattern(), a.p())
163         .appendIf(nf, "uniqueItems", a.uniqueItems() || a.ui())
164         .appendFirst(ne, "type", a.type(), a.t())
165         .appendIf(ne, "$ref", a.$ref())
166      ;
167   }

1214
1215   /**
1216    * Applies targeted {@link Schema} annotations to a {@link org.apache.juneau.Context.Builder}.
1217    */
1218   public static class Apply extends AnnotationApplier<Schema,Context.Builder> {
1219
1220      /**
1221       * Constructor.
1222       *
1223       * @param vr The resolver for resolving values in annotations.
1224       */
1225      public Apply(VarResolverSession vr) {
1226         super(Schema.class, Context.Builder.class, vr);
1227      }
1228
1229      @Override
1230      public void apply(AnnotationInfo<Schema> ai, Context.Builder b) {
1231         Schema a = ai.inner();
1232         if (isEmptyArray(a.on(), a.onClass()))
1233            return;
1234         b.annotations(a);
1235      }
1236   }
